---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie notice"
  description="Praxnote does not use cookies for tracking on the marketing site. Inside the platform, cookies and local storage are used only for session management."
>
  <PageHeader
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Cookie notice"
    lede="Praxnote does not run third-party tracking on the marketing site. Inside the platform, we use cookies and local storage only for session management, never for advertising or cross-site tracking."
  />

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <p class="muted">Last updated: 2026-04-30.</p>

      <h2>Marketing site (praxnote.com)</h2>
      <p>
        The marketing site uses no third-party tracking cookies by default. If we add an
        analytics provider in the future, we'll update this notice and this site, and
        any provider will be configured to respect Do Not Track and to anonymize IP
        addresses.
      </p>

      <h2>The Praxnote platform</h2>
      <p>
        Inside the application, we use cookies and local storage for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>JWT-based session authentication</li>
        <li>CSRF protection</li>
        <li>Language preference (<code>praxnote_portal_lang</code>)</li>
        <li>Theme preference (admin / therapist) for dual-role users</li>
        <li>Local-cache state for the offline vault (when enabled)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not use cookies for cross-site tracking, advertising, or data resale. The
        platform sends no analytics phone-homes by default.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about cookies or the platform's data handling, email
        <a href="mailto:privacy@praxnote.com">privacy@praxnote.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-body { padding: 0 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem); }
  .legal-body h2 { margin: 2rem 0 0.85rem; font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.2vw, 1.7rem); }
  .legal-body p, .legal-body ul { color: var(--stone-700); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 720px; }
  .legal-body ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; }
  code { font-family: ui-monospace, 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace; background: var(--paper-warm); padding: 0.05rem 0.35rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.92em; }
</style>
